  7,69,"wahal 'athar ejbkm 'ana 'anzal allah taealaa 'iilaykum ma ydhkrkm bma fyh alkhayr lkm, ealaa lisan rajul mnkm, taerifun nsbh wsdqh; lykhwwifkm bas allah weqabh? wadhkuruu niemat allah ealaykum 'iidh jaealakum tkhlfwn fi al'ard man qablikum min baed ma 'ahlak qawm nwh, wazad fi ajsamkm quatan wdkhamt, fadhkuruu nieam allah alkathirat elykm; raja' 'ana tfwzu alfawz aleazim fi aldunya walakhrt"
