  7,98,"awamn 'ahl alquraa 'an yatiahum eadhab allah waqt aldahaa, wahum ghafilun mutashaghilun bi'umur dinyahima? wkhss allah hdhyn alwaqatayn bialdhikri, li'ana al'iinsan yakun aghfal ma yakun fihima, famji' aleadhab fihima 'afzae wa'ashada"
