  7,104,"wqal musaa lifireawn mhawrana mbllighana: 'iiniy rswl min allah khaliq alkhalq ajmeyn, wmdbbir ahwalhm wmalhm"
  7,105,"jdyr bi'ana laa 'aqul ealaa allah 'iilaa alhq, whry bi 'ana altzmh, qad jitukum bbrhan whjt bahrt min rabikum ealaa sidq ma 'adhkurah lkm, fatlq -ya frewn- maei bani 'iisrayiyl min 'asrk wqahrk, wkhll sabilahum lebadt allh"
