  7,109,"qal alashraf min qawm frewn: 'iina musaa lasahir yakhudh baeyn alnaas bkhdaeh 'iyahm, hataa yukhayal 'iilayhim 'an aleasa hyt, walshy' bkhlaf ma hu elyh, wahu wasie aleilm balshr mahir bh"
