  7,122,"whw rabi musaa wharwn, wahu aldhy yjb 'an tasrif lah alebadt wahdah dun man swah"
  7,123,"qal fireawn llshrt: amantum biallah qabl 'an adhan lakum bial'iiman bh? 'iina 'iimanikum biallah wtsdyqkm lmwsa w'iqrarkm bnbwth lhylt ahtltmwha 'antum wmwsa; litukhrijuu 'ahl mdyntkm mnha, watakunuu almstathryn bkhyratha, fasawf taelamun -ayha alshrt- ma yhll bikum min aleadhab walnkal"
